Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.70,0:23:26.54,ED CH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\de3}紧握着手中的余温
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.02,0:23:31.69,ED JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\de3}消えない明りを溢す
